OL,3,CFather and son guilty of conspiracy to
OL,4,Cmurder man after clothing store dispute
OL,6,FA father and son have been convicted
OL,7,Fof conspiracy to murder over a plot to
OL,8,Fkill a man in Birmingham.
OL,10,FMohammed Aslam who's 56 and Mohammed
OL,11,FNazir who's 30, from Elms Avenue in
OL,12,FDerby, planned to kill their target
OL,13,Fafter a dispute at a clothing store in
OL,14,FBirmingham in 2018, which left them
OL,15,Fboth injured.JWest Midlands Police say
OL,16,Fthe father and son were determined to
OL,17,Fget revenge and became part of a plan
OL,18,Fto kill the owner of the store, or
OL,19,Ftarget one of his family.
