OL,6,FOn the 7th September 2019, the victim
OL,7,Fdrove home to South Yardley in
OL,8,FBirmingham. As he got out of his car
OL,9,Fhe was threatened with a gun, but he
OL,10,Fescaped after the weapon jammed.
OL,12,FHe then received threatening messages,
OL,13,Fand when he didn't attend a meeting
OL,14,Fwith the group, his house was shot
OL,15,Fthree times.
