OL,6,FPolice say Aslam and Nazir's phones,
OL,7,Falongside CCTV, revealed their
OL,8,Fpreparations and involvement in the
OL,9,Fevents of that night.JBoth men were
OL,10,Fsubject to an investigation by
OL,11,FDerbyshire Police for importing
OL,12,Ffirearms.JWest Midlands Police then
OL,13,Fjoined forces with Derbyshire, linking
OL,14,Fthe different strands of the
OL,15,Finvestigation. The men went on trial
OL,16,Fat Birmingham Crown Court for both
OL,17,Foffences.JOn 5th June 2024, Nazir was
OL,18,Ffound guilty of conspiracy to murder,
OL,19,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,20,Fcause fear of violence.
