OL,6,FDerbyshire Police said: "That nobody
OL,7,Fdied as a result of Aslam and Nazir's
OL,8,Factions is through nothing other than
OL,9,Fsheer good fortune.
OL,11,F"Their plan was to kill and had it not
OL,12,Fbeen for the gun jamming, then there
OL,13,Fis a good chance this would have been
OL,14,Fa murder investigation.
OL,16,F"The importation of firearms is an
OL,17,Fextremely serious offence, and in this
OL,18,Fcase the purpose was to frame their
OL,19,Ftarget in revenge for a previous
OL,20,Fincident.
